org.cloudgraph.hbase.key

Class CompositeRowKeyReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.key.CompositeRowKeyReader

  • public class CompositeRowKeyReader
extends java.lang.Object
    Reads and parses row keys into KeyValue elements where the values can then be found using a given Endpoint and used for syntax tree evaluation, for example.

    For a collection of row keys, for every key in the collection, a client will read a single row key, then collect its values. Endpoints are created on the first row key and used for all additional keys.
    Since:
    1.0.4
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    Endpoint, KeyValue
